---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About | T2H3">
<section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-10">
<div class="rounded-[2rem] border border-red-700/40 bg-black p-10">
<p class="text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-teal-300">About</p>
<h1 class="mt-3 text-5xl font-black text-white">True Trail Hash House Harriers</h1>
<p class="mt-5 text-zinc-300">True Trail Hash House Harriers is a drinking club with a running problem. New hashers are always welcome.</p>
<p class="mt-4 text-zinc-300">At True Trail, we believe the trail is meant to be followed. Checks, false trails and regroups are part of the adventure the hare has created. Shortcutting trail isn't part of our culture—we'd rather solve the trail together and earn the finish.</p>
</div>
</section>
</BaseLayout>
